# **Advanced Task Manager**
--------------------------------------
A modern, feature-rich task management app with multi-user profiles, multiple themes, task details, progress tracking, and image export capabilities. Built with **vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, fully client-side, and deployable on **Vercel**.

🔗 Live Demo: [https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/](https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/)

---

## ✨ Key Features

### 🎨 Multiple Color Themes
- 6 beautiful themes: Default Blue, Forest Green, Sunset Orange, Berry Purple, Ocean Teal, Rose Pink  
- Instant theme switching with a dropdown  
- Theme preference persists across sessions  

### 👤 User Profile System
- Multi-user support: register, switch, and manage accounts  
- 8 customizable avatar emojis  
- Edit profile: name, email, avatar  
- Isolated task lists per user  

### 📋 Enhanced Task Management
- Task details: title, description, category, priority, due date, estimated time  
- Track completion progress (0–100%)  
- 7 categories: Work, Personal, Health, Finance, Learning, Shopping, Travel  
- Smart overdue alerts and visual indicators  
- Inline editing for all task fields  
- Toggle completion, delete tasks individually or all with confirmation  

### 🔍 Advanced Filtering & Sorting
- Status: All, Pending, Completed  
- Category: filter by any of the 7 categories  
- Sort options: Newest, Oldest, Due Date, Priority, A→Z  
- Combined filters with real-time updates  

### 📊 Analytics & Visualization
- Progress bar with task counts and completion percentage  
- Interactive doughnut chart using Chart.js  
- Visual statistics: pending, completed, high/low priority, overdue tasks  

### 📸 Image Export
- Download task list as PNG  
- Export profile card as image  
- Print-ready, professional layouts  

### 📱 Mobile & Accessibility
- Fully responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile  
- Touch-optimized interactions  
- Keyboard shortcuts (e.g., Ctrl+N for new task, ESC to close modals)  
- Accessibility-friendly for screen readers and keyboard navigation  
- Offline ready; works entirely without internet  

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Local Development
1. Clone or download the repository  
2. Open `index.html` in a modern browser  
3. Register or log in as a user  
4. Start managing tasks  

### Deployment on Vercel
1. Push your repository to GitHub  
2. Import the repo on [Vercel](https://vercel.com/)  
3. Deploy instantly as a static site  

---

## 📁 Project Structure
advanced-task-manager/
├── index.html # Main app with UI
├── css/
│ └── style.css # Multiple themes, responsive design
├── js/
│ ├── storage.js # Multi-user localStorage API
│ ├── ui.js # UI rendering, image export, charts
│ └── app.js # App logic, user management
├── libs/
│ └── html2canvas.min.js # Image export library
└── README.md # Documentation


---

## 🔒 Privacy & Security
- Fully client-side: no backend or server required  
- Data stored in **localStorage** per user  
- No external tracking, analytics, or data collection  
- Export options give full control over your data  

---

## 🎯 Performance & Optimization
- Lightweight: <100KB total  
- Smooth rendering with efficient DOM updates  
- Battery- and memory-friendly for mobile devices  
- Fast loading, offline-capable  

---

## 📞 Support & Troubleshooting
- **Reset app**: clear browser localStorage  
- **Enable JS**: must be enabled in browser  
- **Browser**: use modern versions (Chrome, Edge, Firefox)  
- **Console**: check developer console for error messages  

### Known Limitations
- Browser storage limited (~5–10MB)  
- No cloud sync; tasks remain local per device  
- Image download resolution depends on html2canvas  

---

## 🎉 Highlights
- Multi-user profiles with avatars  
- Six beautiful color themes  
- Export tasks and profile as images  
- Enhanced task fields: description, due date, progress tracking  
- Advanced filtering and sorting  
- Improved mobile UX and accessibility  
- Smooth animations and performance optimizations  

